chart.description: Value can be greater than 100% on machine types that allow bursting
chart.name: CPU %
Disk I/O Bytes / min
chart.programText:
A = data('^gcp.gce.disk.io.read.total', rollup='latest').publish(label='A')
B = data('^gcp.gce.disk.io.write.total', rollup='latest').publish(label='B')

chart.name: Network Bytes Out
chart.programText:
A = data('^gcp.gce.network.io.transmit.total', filter=filter('instance_id', '*')).scale(60).publish(label='A', enable=False)
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: CPU % Trend
chart.programText:
A = data('^gcp.gce.cpu.utilization').scale(100).publish(label='A')
B = (A).min().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E', enable=False)
F = (A).max().publish(label='F', enable=False)

chart.name: Disk Metrics 24h Growth %
chart.programText:
A = data('^gcp.gce.disk.io.read.total').sum(by=['sf_metric']).scale(60).mean(over='1h').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).timeshift('1d').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B-1).scale(100).mean(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='C')
A2 = data('^gcp.gce.disk.io.write.total').sum(by=['sf_metric']).scale(60).mean(over='1h').publish(label='A2', enable=False)
B2 = (A2).timeshift('1d').publish(label='B2', enable=False)
C2 = (A2/B2-1).scale(100).mean(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='C2')
A3 = data('^gcp.gce.disk.ops.read.total').sum(by=['sf_metric']).scale(60).mean(over='1h').publish(label='A3', enable=False)
B3 = (A3).timeshift('1d').publish(label='B3', enable=False)
C3 = (A3/B3-1).scale(100).mean(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='C3')
A4 = data('^gcp.gce.disk.ops.write.total').sum(by=['sf_metric']).scale(60).mean(over='1h').publish(label='A4', enable=False)
B4 = (A4).timeshift('1d').publish(label='B4', enable=False)
C4 = (A4/B4-1).scale(100).mean(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='C4')

chart.name: Disk I/O
chart.programText:
A = data('^gcp.gce.disk.ops.read.total', filter=filter('instance_id', '*')).mean(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='A')
B = data('^gcp.gce.disk.ops.write.total', filter=filter('instance_id', '*')).mean(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='B')
C = data('^gcp.gce.disk.io.write.total', filter=filter('instance_id', '*')).mean(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='C')
D = data('^gcp.gce.disk.io.read.total', filter=filter('instance_id', '*')).mean(by=['sf_metric']).publish(label='D')

chart.name: # Disk Operations
chart.programText:
A = data('^gcp.gce.disk.ops.read.total', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('^gcp.gce.disk.ops.write.total', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='B')

chart.description: Delta of bytes written/read to disk
chart.name: Disk I/O
chart.programText:
A = data('^gcp.gce.disk.io.write.total', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('^gcp.gce.disk.io.read.total', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: Network Bytes In
chart.programText:
A = data('^gcp.gce.network.io.receive.total', filter=filter('instance_id', '*')).scale(60).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')
